/**
 * ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
 * NOVA LEARNING OPTIMIZER - META-LEARNING COMPILER (UNIQUE!)
 * ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
 * 
 * Mojo: Fixed optimization pipeline every time
 * Nova: LEARNS which optimizations work best
 * 
 * Gets SMARTER with every compilation! 🧠
